    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You clasp your hands together coating your open palms in a powerful Vaccum. Make a ranged ninjutsu attack on a creature or object in range. On a hit they take 3d6 Wind Damage and must make a Strength saving throw, on a failed save they are pulled towards you and end their movement within 5 feet of you.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast <br />this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu <br />by 3 and the damage by 1d6</p>",
